Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Summer Vacation (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.79,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry Blossom\NJelly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.79,CenterSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Green Tea\NRice Cake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Polka-Dot\NJelly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.79,RightSignLS,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki bean\Nice cream inside
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You drew so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Cat Confection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.80,RightSignMC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Goldfish Jelly\N(soda flavor)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Starry Sky\NGelatin
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.80,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese White-Eye\NConfection
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're so beautiful and look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The striped jelly is cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the jelly balls\Nlook like drops of water, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.94,0:02:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa said we could\Ndo it again next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'd like to do it for the summer festival\Nand New Year's holiday as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I've got this mountain of homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}HEAPING
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All these ideas for sweets\Nare popping up in my head,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a ton of homework and mandatory\Nschool days during summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is actually a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the third-year,\Nbut since a lot of things happened in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,homeroom really fell behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, how old were you when you first\Nwanted to become a professional shogi player?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was in fourth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, I realized\Nthis was the only path left for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was the only thing I knew how to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, you love your Grandpa's shop,\Nso you want to help out there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of things I want to do right now\Nand they're right in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't touch them,\Nwhich makes me feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it's just that I want a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the mountain of homework,\Ntests, entrance exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People say to choose a high school, but I can't\Neven picture myself as a high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know\Nif things will go well for me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Joining another group of people\NI don't know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't really explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina, if you'd like, and if you're free\Nthis Saturday...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers, it's flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice clear day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hoh Hoh Hoh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for inviting us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.75,0:06:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}DEEP BOW
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}YIKES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.42,0:06:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I let my guard down,\Nthe obvious misunderstanding happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. Please enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The theme is\N"Gravity and the Energy of Water."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the culmination of the Shogi Science Club's\Nsummer research project, Flume Noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is the first time I've seen one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Momo!\NThis is flume noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love slippery food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MUHAAA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, part of the bamboo thicket\Nin my yard had to be cut away
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to make room for an addition to my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I better take advantage\Nand make use of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HA\NHA\NHA\NHA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HEAP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.59,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I boiled the noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the first batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Hayashida, let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Thank you for letting us visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.44,0:07:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BOW...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hinata Kawamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, and this is my little sister, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}GASP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}- Hey Hina, I want to eat now!\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the girl Kiriyama was worried about!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sh-She really is cute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kiriyama!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}AWW
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to get things flowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you eat your fill!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Kiriyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's such a cute girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that even a straight-laced guy like Kiriyama\Nwould plunge into the atmosphere of love!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I understand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:07:59.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}JAB JAB
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, it's so bittersweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will I do with him? Sheesh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GRIND GRIND
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida, um, that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking the tempura took a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:27.50,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DISHEVELED
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.50,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SWEAT-\NSOAKED
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for always taking good care of Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you for inviting us here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:53.03,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DEEP\NBOW
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow, tempura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be so pleased.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And how beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has naturally become\Nmore complicated again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, um, Mr. Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}FROZEN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your face looks like it's made of red clay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Hayashida. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is the color of oxidized iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you have heatstroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.95,0:09:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is everybody ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SERIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.29,0:09:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll start with the kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.68,0:09:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}DAZED
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ease up on the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lower the bamboo chute too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The child's eyes can't capture\Nthe noodles properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her eyes are swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a struggle, eh, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of aiming for it,\Nthe trick is to wait for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tempura is yummy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sense of\NAccomplishment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}YES
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! It's now time for the long-awaited...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BA-BAAAM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,starving-man time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SERIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRAB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WHOOSH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}WHIZ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Wait!\N- I can't see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}ZOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got a pink one! I got a pink one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PINK
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Woo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I did it!\N- For pink, you get chicken tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Green! I got a green one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Green is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please go to the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pink one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get my chicken tempura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.52,0:11:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:33.36,DefaultC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SWISH
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NOTHING
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Nothing's flowing down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I got another pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, hey, let me eat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who boiled all these noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Delicious!\N- The chicken tempura is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let me get at least one. Just one is fine!\NLet one come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hayashida, you haven't gotten anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei looks like he's having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice. I didn't know\Nthere were fun high schools like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Chicken tempura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I've got it, Hina.\N- Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Why don't you try to get into this school?\N- I should try to get into this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it's not a green one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Summer Vacation (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}New Year
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SUMIYOSHI SHRINE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Early January of the following year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}Question 30\NUsing the below figure, find ∠x.\NHowever, BA=BC,\Nℓ, m are parallel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Entrance exams are coming up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}STRETCH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HMMMM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}TSUME-SHOGI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey... Um, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}About this figure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SLIDE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for this, you should draw\Nan additional line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}A-Around where should I draw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}First try drawing it\Nin the loneliest-looking spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}COZY\NCOZY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. I decided my first choice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}would be Komahashi Private High School,\Nwhere Rei goes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}He's been helping me study like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I want to go to Hashi High."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first time I said that to Rei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hashi High? Really, Hina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.13,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WHAAAT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:48.64,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WHAAAT
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, he was extremely happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, I don't know if I'll get in yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I haven't even\Nbeen going to a cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The next day,\NRei came over with a "study plan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.78,RightSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIX
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.41,0:15:11.78,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERIOUS
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we start preparing now,\Nyou'll definitely be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since then, he's been supervising my studies\Nseveral times a week after having dinner here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I-I think I'm starting to get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.22,0:15:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah, I think I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right? You can only get a feel for math\Nby solving problems over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine if you stay calm\Nand solve them one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rei is a patient teacher, which makes this\Neasy to understand, and I'm really grateful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:51.70,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZZZ\NZZZ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}PING
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this a late-night snack I'm sensing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:08.09,DefaultLeftM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PEEK
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Do we have anyone here\Nwho would like to be pampered?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GASP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.51,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RATTLE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes, I want to be pampered!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pampered?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STEAMING
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-daaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:36.33,RightSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SIMMER\NSIMMER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:36.33,DefaultLeftM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STEAMING
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fried tofu and tempura together as toppings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SWEET
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is the Kawamoto family's\Nlegendary "Pampered Udon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Melting tempura that's been\Ndeep-fried to fluffiness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,next to sweet fried tofu\Npermeated with sizzling broth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something delicious\Nright next to something delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}MMM...\NHEARTRENDING...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me too happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pampered Udon...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, which do you want with the udon,\Nfried tofu or tempura?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't choose!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, to erase her daughter's troubles,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she came up with\Nthe cockamamie idea of using "both."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She called it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:33.30,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:33.68,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEE\NHEE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:34.26,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HEE\NHEE\NHEE
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pampered Udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom often made it for me as a late-night snack\Nwhen I was studying for entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eating that always made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanted to make it for you when it was\Nyour turn to study for exams, Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:18:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. This makes me happy.\NIt's so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess you have a little longer to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I left the heat on for the bath,\Nso turn it off when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you. Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I first thought I wanted to go\Nto the same private high school as Rei,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was only the feeling of "I want to go."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know if it was okay to be selfish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we set up a stand in the summer,\Nit made me think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.59,0:18:54.59,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BLACK PEARL\NTAPIOCA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:19:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RICE\NFLOUR
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Within these small sweets\Nthat cost 250 yen apiece,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how much time, labor, and money\Nhas gone in to them?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Starting at dawn, Grandpa stands in front of\Nthe stove on days he cooks bean jam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How much money is left for Grandpa\Nfrom one of those sweets?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I went to a private high school,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}how many sweets\Nwould Grandpa have to make?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to Komahashi High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You girls worked really hard\Nwith the stand this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From calculating the cost to production\Nto sales to the end, you did a great job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're worried about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking how much income is left\Nfor Grandpa after making these sweets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Kids don't need to think about that stuff."\NThat's not how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Money is precious. That's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm impressed you realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CLANG
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.29,0:20:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You better not underestimate this Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:57.34,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRIN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:21:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are people waiting for my sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CRESCENT MOON
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I still have plenty of will left\Nto tussle with that bean jam!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go because\Nthat school would be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That one reason is okay by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Whether or not you're enjoying your life\Nis what matters the most to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.57,0:21:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, hey, there's another thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.03,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister and I looked into a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.87,0:21:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Komahashi High School,\Nwhere the kid goes, is really tough to get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}AUGH
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be able to get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, g-good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:43.09,LeftSignM2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHAKE\NSHAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do my best. I'll work hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll study hard and get into that school!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Rei, I've got a question about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:14.25,LeftSignL2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TSUME-SHOGI
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Rei is solving tsume-shogi problems,\Nhe gets quiet and absorbed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The mood was infectious,\Nenabling me to have incredible concentration.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was unusually silent,\Nso I opened the curtain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Outside the window...{\i0}
